<h1 id='screver'>Screver</h1>
<p>Screver is a survey platform for building, distributing, and analyzing customer feedback flows.</p>

<p>This documentation is split into two parts:</p>

<ul>
<li>Public runtime API (<code>/api/v1</code>) for custom clients (web/mobile/embed) that render and submit surveys.</li>
<li>Bearer-protected API (<code>/api/v2</code>) for management, configuration, and integrations.</li>
</ul>

<p>Recommended reading order:</p>

<ol>
<li>Public API (Custom Client)</li>
<li>Authentication (Bearer Token)</li>
<li>Other Bearer-protected sections (<code>Surveys</code>, <code>Survey Items</code>, <code>Survey Results</code>, etc.)</li>
</ol>
